  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cut the cantaloupe and honeydew melon into small cubes.",
    "Brush the flatbread with olive oil and sprinkle with cumin, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Place the flatbread in the air fryer basket and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Remove the flatbread from the air fryer and top with melon cubes.",
    "Sprinkle with chopped parsley and mint.",
    "Return the flatbread to the air fryer and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from the air fryer and let cool for a few minutes before serving."
